update variantenkombis set bestand =
isnull((select COUNT(g.idnr) - kommisioniert as Bestand from geraete g join variante_idnr v on (v.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and v.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and v.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and v.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and v.IDNR=g.IDNR) join KUNDEN k on (k.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and k.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and k.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and k.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and k.KDNR=g.Betreiber) where g.artikelnummer=vk.ArtikelNr and k.Kontoart='W' and g.ModellNummer=:6 and g.Ebene1=:1 and g.Ebene2=:2 and g.Ebene3=:3 and g.Ebene4=:4 and v.Variante1=vk.Var1 and v.Variante2=vk.Var2 and v.Variante3=vk.Var3 and v.Variante4=vk.Var4 and v.Variante5=vk.Var5 group by v.Variante1,v.Variante2,v.Variante3,v.Variante4,v.Variante5),0)
from VariantenKombis vk where vk.Ebene1=:1 and vk.Ebene2=:2 and vk.Ebene3=:3 and vk.Ebene4=:4 and vk.ArtikelNr=':5'
select count(1) from artikel where Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 and bearbeitungsstatus='A' and Internetartikel=1 :5
